net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogthumb.pstatic.net%2FMjAyMDA4MTlfMjU5%2FMDAxNTk3ODA4ODA1Njgx.nPCU7ax6qcUlJvyIEkxuR18nl3iCcbmQK1t08m-hc74g.40eYMyzmAh2xGrakn80ZNPk3hcozw5faFgMClX0BMEog.PNG.isuhani%2Fimage.png%3Ftype%3Dw2%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff120\"}}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0fc21992-0e55-4849-85b7-781a8ca212c7\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c9a9eda2-30ec-48ac-8886-0d44857c5759\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4ffee9d2-3a91-4a07-8562-65841af3b238\"><b>월경통(생리통)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-699b5d41-d3f9-4693-988d-9cf87b5fc2d3\"> </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2ad2beef-2af5-4771-92c2-364f81a4e11c\"><a href=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/222068478227\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/222068478227</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-oglink se-l-image\" id=\"SE-f062a0e5-19fa-4b78-9e2d-851dad732267\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-oglink se-l-image se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-oglink\">\n                                <a href=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/222068478227\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                    <img src=\"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogthumb.pstatic.net%2FMjAyMDA4MjNfMTI3%2FMDAxNTk4MTYwNTI5MTQz.gog4fS5415RtkSDSp4g6qSziMBkmLKycqsCmWVp2gkwg.isY64h6N5fhVPEU6l2FIPIVAAZNYV9xsfGoU0eNM3jMg.JPEG.isuhani%2Fdysmenorrhea2.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw2%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff120\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail-resource\" alt=\"\" />\n                                </a>\n                                <a href=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/222068478227\" class=\"se-oglink-info\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                    <div class=\"se-oglink-info-container\">\n                                        <strong class=\"se-oglink-title\">생리통(월경통 - Dysmenorrhea)의 원인과 치료</strong>\n\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-summary\">우리가 흔히 생리통이라고 말하는 증상의 공식 명칭은 월경통입니다. 그래서 생리통이란 표현대신 월경통이...</p>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-url\">blog.naver.com</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_oglink\", \"id\" :\"SE-f062a0e5-19fa-4b78-9e2d-851dad732267\", \"data\" : {\"link\" : \"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/222068478227\", \"isVideo\" : \"false\", \"thumbnail\" : \"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogthumb.pstatic.net%2FMjAyMDA4MjNfMTI3%2FMDAxNTk4MTYwNTI5MTQz.gog4fS5415RtkSDSp4g6qSziMBkmLKycqsCmWVp2gkwg.isY64h6N5fhVPEU6l2FIPIVAAZNYV9xsfGoU0eNM3jMg.JPEG.isuhani%2Fdysmenorrhea2.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw2%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff120\"}}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e94b4f6b-9c54-4016-b3e6-99ba4c50808a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8464bdd5-d52d-4f6b-8c4f-6982371c891c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-61da72d5-d137-4518-ba7d-9e1915584112\"><b>중풍후유증(뇌경색, 뇌출혈 등 중풍 후 남아있는 후유장애)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1fda9170-00c2-45c6-848c-c82cd137b0d5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8cbdb07b-e259-4df2-863d-08f7a279345a\">에 대한 첩약처방이 건강보험의 적용을 받습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c3b3a265-b22b-4ee9-9dc9-8a8f5a8d3915\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2414d6f1-ce07-476b-8478-0d7ca41b853e\">기존에는 건강보험 적용이 되지 않아서 한약값을 전액 본인이 결제해야 했는데, 이제는 위 3가지 질환(안면마비, 생리통, 중풍후유증)에 대한 첩약은 1년에 한 번 10일분을 원 가격의 50%만 결제하면 되는겁니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e40d8e5e-795d-4e60-bc47-426a54b7eebc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3bd6b277-1b40-4135-96ec-1fef76be2d89\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-39a1b0a1-4387-4b27-add7-cc928b380736\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-39a1b0a1-4387-4b27-add7-cc928b380736\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a87f83c194a57ec2.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a87f83c194a57ec2.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a87f83c194a57ec2.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"739\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8dd959a7-daac-441e-9c07-36ed379cf84c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e3916dd4-4040-41b4-a41c-b01356b51fd2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-81eed2ea-4a97-459e-81d0-22a10d7d5816\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ea48b71d-45f9-4de2-a7e7-c8321ee75512\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-13e8e9e5-72b5-4b22-b857-2c8dc545ae2b\">또 한가지! </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aa098925-4d65-46dc-b89c-126609277b5e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2f3c3a96-616e-4e11-b962-c42ce663de4a\">건강보험 적용이 되기 때문에 실비(실손)보험 혜택도 받을 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a8f3bbb9-b736-43fa-9a2a-e97a17abcfa8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f262cb5b-ec03-4f8e-9c53-1b600d0e8027\">1년에 1번, 1인당 10일분의 한약이 50% 본인부담금으로 처방받을 수 있는건데요, 10일분 이상 더 길게 처방받아서 복용해야 하는경우에도 실비 보험을 적용받을 수 있습니다. 자세한 내용은 이수한의원에 문의하세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1f5dafdc-93d9-4d12-9841-fb5ef374272d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-539bf6b6-898d-4cde-9ba1-9c79d9dfcd69\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7b66ad5e-38f8-4c32-9795-89e40b299940\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7b66ad5e-38f8-4c32-9795-89e40b299940\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6a3e3835f576724a.png\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6a3e3835f576724a.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6a3e3835f576724a.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"707\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8ceae9c4-983c-4b18-bc35-bfd2d4849363\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-secti